<Worksheet ss:Name="Arranged Test Cases"><Table>
<Column ss:Width="420"/><Column ss:Width="560"/><Column ss:Width="560"/>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Test Case Title</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Steps</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Expected Result</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement is auto-generated once per day at scheduled time</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Scheduler configuration is available. 2. Eligible merchant transactions are imported for the active POS. 3. POS Statement generation is configured.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Wait for configured scheduler time and verify output directory or configured statement directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated automatically once per day for the active POS where eligible transactions are imported today.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement is generated when scheduler is manually triggered</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. POS has eligible imported merchant transactions. 2. Manual scheduler trigger option is available.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Manually trigger the POS statement scheduler and verify generated output in configured statement directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated successfully when scheduler is triggered manually.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement file name</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. POS has eligible imported transactions. 2. POS statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the generated POS statement file name.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement file name should follow the configured naming convention consistently.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement is generated in the configured Statement Directory from POS Setup</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS is in Live status, Statement Directory is configured in POS Setup, and eligible transactions exist for statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger or wait for POS statement generation and verify the generated file location.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated in the Statement Directory configured in POS Setup.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement is generated in the live Statement Directory when review entry exists with updated Statement Directory</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS is available in Live with an approved Statement Directory and a Review entry exists where Statement Directory is updated but not yet approved.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger or wait for POS statement generation and verify the generated file location.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated in the currently approved Live Statement Directory, not the pending Review directory.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement and Merchant Statement are generated in updated Statement Directory after checker approval</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Statement Directory is updated by Maker in POS Setup and the update is approved by Checker. Eligible transactions exist for statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger or wait for POS and Merchant statement generation and verify the generated file locations.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Both POS Statement and Merchant Statement should be generated in the latest approved updated Statement Directory.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify no POS Statement generation when there is no transaction for any merchant under the POS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS exists but no transaction is available for any merchant linked to that POS for the statement date.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement generation when transaction exists for one merchant only under the POS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS has transaction data for only one merchant.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and open the generated workbook.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated successfully and only the relevant merchant should appear.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify no POS Statement generation when POS status is Inactive in POS Setup</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS status is Inactive in POS Setup and transactions may exist for linked merchants.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation for the inactive POS.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement generation when POS status is updated from Inactive to Active</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS status was previously Inactive and is updated to Active in POS Setup. Eligible merchant transactions exist for the POS.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Update POS status from Inactive to Active, trigger or wait for statement generation, and open generated POS statement.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated successfully once the POS is active and should contain eligible merchant transaction data.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when only QRT file is uploaded</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Only QRT file is uploaded. 2. QRC file is not uploaded. 3. QRT Refund file is not uploaded.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify output directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when only QRC file is uploaded</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Only QRC file is uploaded. 2. QRT file is not uploaded. 3. QRT Refund file is not uploaded.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify output directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when only QRT Refund file is uploaded</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Only QRT Refund file is uploaded. 2. QRT file is not uploaded. 3. QRC file is not uploaded.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify output directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRT file status is PENDING</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT file status is PENDING. 2. Other required files may exist.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRC file status is PENDING</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRC file status is PENDING. 2. Other required files may exist.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRT Refund file status is PENDING</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT Refund file status is PENDING. 2. Other required files may exist based on business rule.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRT file status is FAILED</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT file status is FAILED. 2. Other dependent files may exist.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify output or file processing behavior.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRC file status is FAILED</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRC file status is FAILED. 2. Other dependent files may exist.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify output or file processing behavior.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRT Refund file status is FAILED</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT Refund file status is FAILED. 2. Other dependent files may exist.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify output or file processing behavior.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRT file status is FAILED but some batches are imported</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT file batch import is partial. 2. Final QRT file status is FAILED. 3. QRC may be imported successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated even if some QRT batches were imported.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRC file status is FAILED but some batches are imported</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRC file batch import is partial. 2. Final QRC file status is FAILED. 3. QRT may be imported successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated even if some QRC batches were imported.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no POS statement generation when QRT Refund file status is FAILED but some batches are imported</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT Refund file batch import is partial. 2. Final QRT Refund file status is FAILED. 3. QRT and QRC may be imported successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated even if some QRT Refund batches were imported.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Summary header section values in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully for a POS with valid transaction data.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the POS Summary sheet and verify POS Partner Name, Merchant ID, Transaction Date, and Total No. of Transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All header values should match the actual POS statement generation data.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify processed and pending total summary values in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully with both processed and pending merchant transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the POS Summary sheet and verify processed and pending values for Total Transaction Amount, Total MDR Charges, Total Refund Amount, Total Pending Previous Charges, and Total Payable Amount.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each processed and pending total should equal the sum of the corresponding merchant rows.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Processed Merchant Transaction Summary row values in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully with processed merchant transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify each processed row for Outlet ID, Merchant Name, Total Transaction Amount, Total MDR Amount, Total Refund Amount, Total Pending Previous Charges, and Total Payable Amount.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each processed merchant row value should match the linked merchant transaction sheet.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Pending Merchant Transaction Summary row values in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully with pending merchant transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify each pending row for Outlet ID, Merchant Name, Total Transaction Amount, Total MDR Amount, Total Refund Amount, Total Pending Previous Charges, and Total Payable Amount.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each pending merchant row value should match the linked merchant transaction sheet.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup summary values in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully and at least one transaction exists where cashier ID is not linked to any merchant for that POS.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup values for Total Transaction Amount, Total MDR Amount, Total Refund Amount, Total Payable Amount, Total No. of Transactions, and STATUS.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each value should match the transactions without cashier ID setup.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify formatting consistency for transaction count values in POS Summary</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify all transaction count fields.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Transaction counts should be displayed as whole numbers without incorrect decimals.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify hyperlink navigation from POS Summary and Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully with outlet hyperlinks and Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup hyperlink.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Click an Outlet ID under Processed Merchant Transaction Summary, an Outlet ID under Pending Merchant Transaction Summary, and Total No. of Transactions under Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each hyperlink should navigate to the correct detailed sheet.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement sheet names are generated correctly for all merchant outlets</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS statement contains multiple outlet sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open workbook and compare outlet IDs in summary with sheet names.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Sheet names should correctly map to the respective Outlet ID values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify broken hyperlink does not exist for any Outlet ID in POS Summary</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS statement is generated with multiple outlet rows.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Click each Outlet ID in processed and pending sections.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Every hyperlink should navigate successfully to the correct merchant sheet.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify broken hyperlink does not exist for TWC transaction count</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS statement contains TWC summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Click Total No. of Transactions in TWC section.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Hyperlink should navigate successfully to the correct TWC detail sheet.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchant transactions are processed</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully and all merchant transactions for the POS are in PROCESSED status.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify Processed Merchant Transaction Summary and Pending Merchant Transaction Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Processed section should be populated correctly and Pending section should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchant transactions are pending</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully and all merchant transactions for the POS are in PENDING status.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify Pending Merchant Transaction Summary and Processed Merchant Transaction Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Pending section should be populated correctly and Processed section should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when few merchant transactions are processed and few are pending</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully and the POS contains both PROCESSED and PENDING merchant transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify both processed and pending totals and merchant rows.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Both sections should be populated correctly and should reconcile with merchant sheets.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify same merchant can appear in both processed and pending summaries when transactions exist in both statuses</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: One merchant has both processed and pending transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify the same merchant across both sections.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">The same merchant should appear in both sections with status-specific values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify merchant appears in correct status section based on transaction status</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS contains merchants with processed and pending transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and compare merchant row placement with merchant transaction sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant should appear under the correct status section.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchants have positive settlement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All merchants under the POS have valid positive settlement transactions and POS Statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify Processed Merchant Transaction Summary, Pending Merchant Transaction Summary, and Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All merchant rows should appear under Processed Merchant Transaction Summary. Pending Merchant Transaction Summary should display No Records Found with merged cells. Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup should display No Records Found if no unmapped cashier transaction exists.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify processed totals and drill down to each merchant sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary totals should equal the sum of all merchant sheet processed values, and each merchant sheet should show positive settlement values correctly.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchants have zero settlement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All merchants under the POS have only zero settlement transactions and POS Statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify section placement.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All merchant rows should appear under Processed Merchant Transaction Summary if zero settlement is treated as processed by business rule. Pending Merchant Transaction Summary should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify merchant row values and merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each merchant row and respective merchant sheet should show zero settlement values correctly, including payable amount and remarks based on business rule.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchants have negative settlement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All merchants under the POS have only negative settlement transactions and POS Statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify section placement.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All merchant rows should appear under Pending Merchant Transaction Summary. Processed Merchant Transaction Summary should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify pending totals and merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Pending totals should equal the sum of all merchant pending values, and each merchant sheet should show negative settlement records with correct status and remarks.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchants have negative settlement with previous pending charges</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All merchants under the POS have negative settlement and previous pending charges, and POS Statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify Pending Merchant Transaction Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All merchant rows should appear under Pending Merchant Transaction Summary with previous pending charges populated correctly. Processed Merchant Transaction Summary should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify total pending previous charges and payable amount against merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary pending totals should reconcile with all merchant sheets, including previous pending charges in the payable calculation.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchants have pending settlement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All merchants under the POS have pending settlement transactions and POS Statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify section placement.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All merchant rows should appear under Pending Merchant Transaction Summary. Processed Merchant Transaction Summary should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify pending values and merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Pending totals should match the merchant rows and merchant sheets for transaction amount, MDR, refund, previous pending charges, and payable amount based on business rule.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all merchants have pending settlement with previous pending charges</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All merchants under the POS have pending settlement and previous pending charges, and POS Statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify pending summary values.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All merchant rows should appear under Pending Merchant Transaction Summary and previous pending charges should be populated correctly. Processed Merchant Transaction Summary should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Compare totals with merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Pending totals, including previous pending charges and payable amount, should match the respective merchant sheets.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when few merchants have positive negative zero pending and pending with previous pending charges</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement is generated successfully and different merchants under the same POS have a mix of positive, negative, zero, pending, and pending with previous pending charges scenarios.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify merchant placement under processed and pending sections.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchants with positive and zero settlement should appear under the correct processed section based on business rule. Merchants with negative settlement, pending settlement, and pending with previous pending charges should appear under the pending section.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify processed totals and pending totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each section total should equal the sum of its respective merchant rows.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Drill down into each merchant sheet and compare row values with POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each merchant row in POS Summary should match its respective merchant transaction sheet, including previous pending charges and payable values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement handles merchant with zero payable amount correctly</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: One merchant has zero payable amount.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify merchant row and totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Zero payable amount should be displayed correctly at merchant level and summary level.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement handles merchant with negative payable amount correctly</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: One merchant has negative payable amount.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify merchant row and totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Negative payable amount should be displayed correctly and included properly in totals.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when few merchant transactions are processed few are pending and few are without cashier ID setup</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully and the POS contains processed, pending, and cashier-unmapped transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify processed summary, pending summary, and Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each section should contain only its applicable transactions and values should reconcile correctly.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement when all transactions are without cashier ID setup</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement report is generated successfully and all transactions for the POS have cashier IDs not linked to any merchant.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and verify Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup, Processed Merchant Transaction Summary, and Pending Merchant Transaction Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">TWC should be populated with all transactions and both merchant summary sections should display No Records Found with merged cells.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify TWC section shows No Records Found when no cashier setup issue exists</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: All cashier IDs are properly linked.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and open POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup should display No Records Found with merged cells across all columns.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify not configured Cashier ID transactions are excluded from merchant sheets and included only in TWC</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT file is uploaded with valid and invalid cashier IDs. 2. QRC file is uploaded. 3. POS statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS statement and compare merchant sheets with Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup section.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Transactions with not configured cashier IDs should not appear in merchant sheets and should appear only in Transaction Without Cashier ID Setup.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Summary total number of transactions reconciles with processed pending and TWC sections combined</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS statement contains processed, pending, and TWC data.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and sum transaction counts from processed, pending, and TWC sections.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Overall Total No. of Transactions should reconcile with all applicable sections combined.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement values match source transaction report totals</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Source transaction report and POS statement are generated from same data set.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Compare source transaction totals with POS statement totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should match the eligible source transaction totals exactly.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify all imported eligible POS merchant transactions are included in the statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Multiple eligible transactions are imported for merchants under the POS for the same transaction date. 2. POS statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the generated POS statement and compare imported transactions against merchant sheets and POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All imported eligible POS merchant transactions should be present and displayed in ascending order of transaction date and time.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify merchant summary and detail values in Merchant Statement match the respective merchant summary and merchant transaction sheet in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Merchant statement and POS statement are generated successfully for the same transaction set.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open Merchant Statement and POS Statement for the same merchant and compare summary and detail values.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant Statement values should match the respective merchant summary row and merchant sheet values in POS Statement.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Merchant Statement count matches the number of merchant summaries and merchant sheets in POS Statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement and Merchant Statements are generated successfully for the same POS and transaction set.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Statement, count applicable merchant summaries, count merchant sheets, count generated Merchant Statements, and compare all counts.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant Statement count should match the number of applicable merchant summaries and merchant transaction sheets based on the business rule.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify merchant statement count matches unique merchant summaries and merchant sheets in POS statement when one merchant appears in both processed and pending</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Same merchant appears in both processed and pending sections in POS statement. 2. Merchant statements are generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Count unique merchant summaries, merchant sheets, and generated merchant statements.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant statement count should match unique merchant or outlet count and should not be duplicated due to appearance in both processed and pending sections.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement generation when merchant name is updated</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Merchant name is updated before statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and verify merchant name in summary and detail sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Latest approved merchant name should be reflected consistently in the statement.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement generation when outlet mapping changes before statement generation</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Outlet mapping is updated before statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and verify summary row and sheet mapping.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Statement should reflect the latest valid outlet mapping at generation time.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Partner Name and Merchant ID in POS Statement after maker update is checker approved</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Maker has updated POS Partner Name and or Merchant ID, and Checker has approved the update.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement after approval and verify POS Partner Name and Merchant ID in POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary should display the latest approved values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Partner Name and Merchant ID in POS Statement when pending update record exists</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Partner Name and or Merchant ID are updated by Maker, but Checker approval is still pending in Review.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement while update is pending and verify POS Partner Name and Merchant ID in POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary should display the currently approved Live values, not the pending updated values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Outlet ID and Merchant Name in POS Summary after update is checker approved</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Maker has updated Outlet ID and or Merchant Name, and Checker has approved the update.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement after approval and verify Outlet ID and Merchant Name in POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary should display the latest approved values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Outlet ID and Merchant Name in POS Summary when pending update record exists</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Outlet ID and or Merchant Name are updated by Maker, but Checker approval is pending.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement while update is pending and verify Outlet ID and Merchant Name in POS Summary.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary should display the currently approved Live values, not the pending values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Merchant Name, Merchant Outlet Name and Merchant ID in merchant sheet after update is checker approved</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Maker has updated Merchant Name, Merchant Outlet Name, and or Merchant ID, and Checker has approved the update.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement after approval and verify Merchant Name, Merchant Outlet Name, and Merchant ID in the merchant sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant sheet should display the latest approved values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify Merchant Name, Merchant Outlet Name and Merchant ID in merchant sheet when pending update record exists</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Merchant Name, Merchant Outlet Name, and or Merchant ID are updated by Maker, but Checker approval is pending.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement while update is pending and verify Merchant Name, Merchant Outlet Name, and Merchant ID in the merchant sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant sheet should display the currently approved Live values, not the pending updated values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify updated POS Setup and Merchant Setup values are reflected together after checker approval</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. POS Setup and Merchant Setup values are updated by Maker. 2. Checker has approved the updates before statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and verify updated values in POS Summary and merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Statement should display the latest approved POS and Merchant setup values consistently.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify pending setup updates are not reflected in POS statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. POS Setup and or Merchant Setup values are updated by Maker. 2. Checker approval is still pending in Review.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement while updates are still pending and verify values in summary and merchant sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Statement should use only Live approved values and should not display pending Review values.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement is not generated with duplicate merchant rows for same outlet</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS statement is generated for a POS with transactions for the same outlet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open POS Summary and review processed and pending merchant rows.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Same Outlet ID should not appear as duplicate within the same status section unless business rule explicitly allows it.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement does not include merchant not linked to the POS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Transactions exist for merchants outside the POS.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and review merchant rows and drill-down sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Only merchants linked to the selected POS should be included in the statement.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify duplicate transaction in QRT file is considered only once based on older Transaction Date and Time</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT file contains duplicate transaction records for the same transaction reference with different Transaction Date and Time. 2. Related QRC data is uploaded. 3. POS statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the POS statement and verify detail rows and summary totals for the duplicate transaction.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Duplicate transaction should be considered only once based on the older Transaction Date and Time, and totals should reflect only that valid record.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify duplicate refund transaction in QRT Refund file is considered only once based on latest Refund Date and Time</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRT Refund file contains duplicate refund records for the same transaction with different Refund Date and Time. 2. POS statement is generated successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the POS statement and verify refund detail rows and refund totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Duplicate refund transaction should be considered only once based on the latest Refund Date and Time.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify duplicate QRC transaction in same file is considered only once</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. QRC file contains duplicate transaction records for the same transaction reference number within the same file. 2. Related QRT file is uploaded successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and verify mapped MDR values and totals for the duplicate transaction.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Only one valid mapped transaction should be considered and statement totals should not be duplicated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify duplicate QRC transaction from another file is considered based on first valid imported record</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. First QRC file with valid transaction is uploaded successfully. 2. Second QRC file contains the same duplicate transaction reference number. 3. Related QRT file is uploaded successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate POS statement and verify the mapped MDR values for the duplicate transaction reference.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should reflect only the first valid imported QRC transaction mapping.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify no POS Statement generation on next day when all transactions are imported after scheduled time of POS statement generation</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Transactions are imported on the current day only after the POS statement generation scheduled time.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Allow scheduled generation to pass and verify statement generation for next day.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should not be generated on next day for transactions imported after the scheduled cutoff.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify multiple POS Statement generation when one merchant has transactions with multiple transaction dates on the same day</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: One merchant under a POS has transactions belonging to multiple transaction dates within the same day processing cycle.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Multiple POS statements should be generated correctly according to transaction date grouping rules.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify multiple POS Statement generation when multiple merchants have transactions with multiple transaction dates on the same day</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: Multiple merchants under a POS have transactions belonging to multiple transaction dates within the same day processing cycle.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Multiple POS statements should be generated correctly according to transaction date grouping rules for all applicable merchants.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no duplicate POS statement generation for same POS and transaction date</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. POS is Active. 2. Transactions are already imported for a transaction date. 3. POS statement has already been generated once for that POS and transaction date.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger the scheduler again for the same POS and transaction date and verify output and processing behavior.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Duplicate POS statement should not be generated for the same POS and transaction date.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify only current day POS statement is generated when previous day QRT file is uploaded after scheduled time and current day QRT file is uploaded</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Previous day QRT data is uploaded only after previous day scheduled time. 2. Current day QRT file is uploaded before current day scheduled time. 3. POS is Active.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify generated statement files after current day scheduler run.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Only current day POS statement should be generated and previous day statement should not be back-generated in current day cycle.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify duplicate transaction reference number in next day QRT file is not included when already considered in previous day POS statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Previous day POS statement is generated successfully and includes a valid transaction reference number. 2. Next day QRT file contains the same duplicate transaction reference number.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate next day POS statement and verify detail rows and totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Next day POS statement should exclude the duplicate transaction reference already considered in previous day statement.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify duplicate refund transaction reference number in next day QRT Refund file is not included when already considered in previous day POS statement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Previous day POS statement is generated successfully and includes a valid refund transaction reference number. 2. Next day QRT Refund file contains the same duplicate refund transaction reference number.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Generate next day POS statement and verify refund detail rows and totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Next day POS statement should exclude the duplicate refund transaction reference already considered in previous day statement.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify no conflict when POS or Merchant status is updated to Inactive while POS statement processing is already pending</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. POS statement processing request is already in progress or pending in the processing layer. 2. POS or Merchant status is updated from Active to Inactive during processing.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Monitor in-progress statement processing and verify the final outcome.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">In-progress POS statement should complete based on existing job context without system conflict or corrupt output.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_Verify POS Statement generation for large volume of merchants and transactions</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS has large number of merchants and transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger statement generation and review workbook completeness and totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Statement should generate successfully with complete data and correct totals.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement generation with bulk uploaded transaction records</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: 1. Bulk QRT transaction records are uploaded for merchants under the POS. 2. Related QRC and QRT Refund data are uploaded.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Required setup is available.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger POS statement generation and verify workbook completeness, detail rows, totals, and behavior.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement should be generated successfully without truncation, corruption, missing records, or incorrect totals under bulk volume.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement split generation when merchant count equals configured merchant sheet limit</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS is Active; application config has merchant sheet limit configured as 500; POS has exactly 500 eligible merchants with transactions for the same transaction date; QRT and QRC files are imported successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger the POS Statement generation scheduler.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Statement generation should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the generated POS statement files in the configured Statement Directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Only one POS statement file should be generated because merchant count is equal to the configured merchant sheet limit.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the generated POS statement file and verify merchant transaction sheets.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">All 500 merchant transaction sheets should be available in the same POS statement file.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement split generation when merchant count is one more than configured merchant sheet limit</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS is Active; application config has merchant sheet limit configured as 500; POS has 501 eligible merchants with transactions for the same transaction date; QRT and QRC files are imported successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger the POS Statement generation scheduler.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Statement generation should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify generated POS statement file count.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Two POS statement files should be generated.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify merchant sheets in the first generated POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">First POS statement file should contain merchant transaction sheets up to the configured merchant sheet limit.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify merchant sheets in the second generated POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Second POS statement file should contain the remaining one merchant transaction sheet.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement split generation when merchant count exceeds configured merchant sheet limit</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS is Active; application config has merchant sheet limit configured as 500; POS has 501 eligible merchants with transactions for the same transaction date; QRT and QRC files are imported successfully; POS Statement scheduler is available.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger the POS Statement generation scheduler manually or wait for the scheduled time.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Statement generation should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the generated POS statement files in the configured Statement Directory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Multiple POS statement files should be generated because merchant count exceeds the configured merchant sheet limit.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the first POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">First file should contain the POS Summary sheet and merchant transaction sheets up to the configured merchant sheet limit.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the additional POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Additional file should contain the remaining merchant transaction sheet(s) which exceed the configured merchant sheet limit.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify all merchant transaction sheets across all generated POS statement files.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each eligible merchant should have one respective merchant transaction sheet across the generated files without missing or duplicate merchant sheets.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify navigation link behavior when merchant sheet is available in the same split POS statement file</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement is generated for more than the configured merchant sheet limit and multiple POS statement files are created.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the POS Summary sheet in the first generated POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary sheet should open successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Click the Outlet ID link for a merchant whose transaction sheet is available in the same first POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">User should be navigated to the respective merchant transaction sheet within the same POS statement file.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify navigation link is not available when merchant sheet is generated in another split POS statement file</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement is generated for more than the configured merchant sheet limit and merchant transaction sheets are split across multiple POS statement files.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the POS Summary sheet in the first generated POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary sheet should open successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the Outlet ID value for a merchant whose transaction sheet is generated in another POS statement file.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Outlet ID should be displayed as text without navigation hyperlink in the first POS statement file.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the respective additional POS statement file and verify the merchant transaction sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant transaction sheet should be available in the respective additional POS statement file.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement split file name format</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement is generated for more than the configured merchant sheet limit and multiple POS statement files are created.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the generated POS statement file names.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">File name should follow the format DNQR POS Transaction Report_&lt;Transaction Date&gt;_&lt;MerchantID&gt;_&lt;POSName&gt;_&lt;Current excel count&gt;of&lt;No. of Excel&gt;.xlsx.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the first generated POS statement file name.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">First file name should contain 1of&lt;No. of Excel&gt;.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify the last generated POS statement file name.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Last file name should contain &lt;No. of Excel&gt;of&lt;No. of Excel&gt;.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify Transaction Date, Merchant ID, and POS Name in all split POS statement file names.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Transaction Date, Merchant ID, and POS Name should remain the same across all split POS statement files; only the excel count should differ.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS statement split generation based on updated configured merchant sheet limit</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS is Active; merchant sheet limit is updated in application config to a value other than 500; POS has merchant count greater than the updated configured limit; QRT and QRC files are imported successfully.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Trigger the POS Statement generation scheduler after the updated configuration is effective.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Statement generation should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify generated POS statement file count.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS statement files should be split based on the updated configured merchant sheet limit, not based on the old limit.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify merchant transaction sheet distribution across the generated files.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Each file should contain merchant sheets within the updated configured limit, and remaining merchants should be carried to the next generated file.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">QRS_BO Portal_POS Statement_Verify POS summary values remain correct when merchant sheets are split across multiple POS statement files</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition: POS Statement is generated for more than the configured merchant sheet limit and multiple POS statement files are created with processed, pending, and refund transactions.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Precondition should be completed successfully.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Open the first POS statement file and verify POS Summary totals.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">POS Summary totals should be calculated for all eligible merchants belonging to the POS statement scope as per design, including merchants whose sheets are available in other split files if they are displayed in the summary.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify merchant summary rows in the POS Summary sheet.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Merchant summary row values should match the respective merchant transaction sheet values across the split POS statement files.</Data></Cell></Row>
<Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Verify total merchant coverage across all split files.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Cell"><Data ss:Type="String">Combined merchant transaction sheets across all generated files should reconcile with the merchant summary records and source transactions.</Data></Cell></Row>
</Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><FreezePanes/><FrozenNoSplit/><SplitHorizontal>1</SplitHorizontal><TopRowBottomPane>1</TopRowBottomPane><ActivePane>2</ActivePane></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>
